snippet.title: maybe: Interactive Stories | My Ex is So into Me Ep 1
snippet.description:
Right before signing the contract of your lifetime, you meet two of your ex-boyfriends. One is your unforgettable first love from 10 years ago, and the other is your second love, with whom you had an intense break-up. Will you be able to fall in love again?
.
.
Scenario by Aria / Artwork by yanggae / Original Novels from NAVER SERIES (©hada, smiling)
.
